{"tid":2352972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自由黨：政府又話盈餘唔得搞得 咁不如拎外匯儲備2千億洗下先","createTime":"2021-01-04T11:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T12:00:52.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ca06629ab5d34fa217f158df69c714704595d3","tid":2352972,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"自由黨倡預算案動用外匯基金2000億元滾存盈餘救市<br />\n<br />\n自由黨立法會議員與財政司長陳茂波會面，要求政府由外匯基金累計盈餘，撥出2000億元，推行第5輪防疫抗疫基金，相信可以支援不同行為的同時，可以減輕財赤壓力，亦不會影響金融體系穩定。他們又建議政府補貼商業借貸利息2厘，重推保就業計劃，寬免或減低政府商業收費和牌照費，在疫情緩和後派發電子消費券。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨黨魁鍾國斌指，疫情未見遏止，對各行各業造成前所未見影響，結業潮一觸即發，現時是抗疫救市的關鍵時刻，政府必須要靈活變通，盡量動用可用資源，保企業，保就業。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2373390&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=f9c47d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373390</a>"},{"pid":"8aec6dd8129320e5a32e2626270f164a73d32cce","tid":2352972,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"唔駛講咁多廢話，比返老強出黎"},{"pid":"ec82db31ed74648f2e0ca5290c1813614ac3763c","tid":2352972,"uid":323157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df31f7bd056643b16fccbfee18442a6c66debe40","tid":2352972,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"777:股市會跌,不了(大鱷)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2025b019c04f8afce0b7fb38b7390da91c95fb9","tid":2352972,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df31f7bd056643b16fccbfee18442a6c66debe40","tid":2352972,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"777:股市會跌,不了(大鱷)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB